{"tid":345180,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【李華華搶先睇】一萬蚊請到執董 幸福投資真幸福","createTime":"2017-08-02T22:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T23:22:42.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a67a863f7761afdbe24d5f2fa58fb2f854bdc14","tid":345180,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T22:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170802/large/1501681093_3d4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170802%2Flarge%2F1501681093_3d4d.jpg&h=21af2907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上市公司高薪請「自己人」或「無履歷妙齡少女」做執行董事就聽得多，但噚日喺創業板上市嘅中國幸福投資(8116)公佈，月薪一萬，就請到位有8年工作經驗嘅人做集團執行董事。<br />\n<br />\n公告話，呢位執董叫李嘉琪，芳齡30，持有暨南大學英語商業管理理學士學位及專業秘書及管理訓練證書，同時持有WSET葡萄酒及烈酒第二級證書，於公共關係範疇擁有逾8年經驗，並於旅遊及私人飛機管理及安排範疇擁有逾5年經驗，委任即日生效。<br />\n<br />\n中國幸福投資從事銷售紅酒、雪茄及高爾夫產品，賣嘅都係貴價用品，但李嘉琪年薪12萬元，即係一個月一萬蚊咋，家陣請個洗碗工都唔得喇。<br />\n<br />\n有機會真係想問問李小姐，假假地都大學畢業(唔好理乜大學)，工作經驗又豐富，點解咁抵得諗，用「優惠價」做呢份工。需知道，上市公司執董職責好繁重，好多責任要負㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57033932&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57033932%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170802&d=zKJH1oXzmgmdq2H9ic6TfNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=024ced9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57033932%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170802&h=08fe9a77\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57033932&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170802</a>"},{"pid":"3741f82c4fcf6e4ef94136a1debad4400667b5db","tid":345180,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T23:22:42.000Z","msg":"李生 1蚊tim <br />\n人地唔係打工仔<br />\n係老闆"}]}